query: select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent, 'Паспорт РФ' + ' ' + IDoc.Serie + ' ' + IDoc.Number OR1 from PersonCards PerC join IdentityDocs IDoc on PerC.IdentityDocId = IDoc.UniqueId where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and IDoc.DocType = 1 and len(IDoc.Serie) > 0 and len(IDoc.Number) > 0

select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent, 'Военный билет' + ' ' + IDoc.Serie + ' ' + IDoc.Number OR1 from PersonCards PerC join IdentityDocs IDoc on PerC.IdentityDocId = IDoc.UniqueId where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and IDoc.DocType = 2 and len(IDoc.Serie) > 0 and len(IDoc.Number) > 0

select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent, 'Загранпаспорт РФ' + ' ' + IDoc.Serie + ' ' + IDoc.Number OR1 from PersonCards PerC join IdentityDocs IDoc on PerC.IdentityDocId = IDoc.UniqueId where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and IDoc.DocType = 3 and len(IDoc.Serie) > 0 and len(IDoc.Number) > 0

select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent, 'Паспорт СССР' + ' ' + substring(IDoc.Serie, 1, 2) + '-' + substring(IDoc.Serie, 3, 2) + ' ' + IDoc.Number OR1 from PersonCards PerC join IdentityDocs IDoc on PerC.IdentityDocId = IDoc.UniqueId where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and IDoc.DocType = 4 and len(IDoc.Serie) = 4 and len(IDoc.Number) > 0

select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent, 'Иные документы' + ' ' + IDoc.Serie + ' ' + IDoc.Number OR1 from PersonCards PerC join IdentityDocs IDoc on PerC.IdentityDocId = IDoc.UniqueId where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and IDoc.DocType = 5 and len(IDoc.Serie) > 0 and len(IDoc.Number) > 0

select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent, 'Св-во о рождении' + ' ' + substring(IDoc.Serie, 1, 1) + '-' + substring(IDoc.Serie, 2, 2) + ' ' + IDoc.Number OR1 from PersonCards PerC join IdentityDocs IDoc on PerC.IdentityDocId = IDoc.UniqueId where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and IDoc.DocType = 6 and len(IDoc.Serie) > 0 and len(IDoc.Number) > 0

select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent, case when IDoc.DocType = 1 then 'Паспорт РФ' when IDoc.DocType = 2 then 'Военный билет' when IDoc.DocType = 3 then 'Загранпаспорт РФ' when IDoc.DocType = 4 then 'Паспорт СССР' when IDoc.DocType = 5 then 'Иные документы' when IDoc.DocType = 6 then 'Св-во о рождении' end + ' ' + IDoc.Number OR1 from PersonCards PerC join IdentityDocs IDoc on PerC.IdentityDocId = IDoc.UniqueId where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and len(IDoc.Serie) = 0 and len(IDoc.Number) > 0

select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent, case when IDoc.DocType = 1 then 'Паспорт РФ' when IDoc.DocType = 2 then 'Военный билет' when IDoc.DocType = 3 then 'Загранпаспорт РФ' when IDoc.DocType = 4 then 'Паспорт СССР' when IDoc.DocType = 5 then 'Иные документы' when IDoc.DocType = 6 then 'Св-во о рождении' end + ' ' + IDoc.Serie OR1 from PersonCards PerC join IdentityDocs IDoc on PerC.IdentityDocId = IDoc.UniqueId where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and len(IDoc.Serie) > 0 and len(IDoc.Number) = 0
select top(1) PerC.UniqueId Ent, '' OR1 from PersonCards PerC where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and PerC.IdentityDocId is null
